<div id="pf4" class="pf w0 h7" data-page-no="4"><div class="pc pc4 w0 h7"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h8" alt="" src="bg4.png"/><div class="t m97 x11 h16 y7b ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meet the </div><div class="t m98 x34 h16 y7c ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Author of </div><div class="t m7c x34 h16 y7d ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This </div><div class="t m99 x34 h16 y7e ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Quarter&apos;s </div><div class="t m9a x11 h16 y7f ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons </div><div class="t m9b x35 h17 y80 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Russell Holt is associate editor of </div><div class="t m9c x36 h17 y80 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Signs of the Times. </div><div class="t m9d x15 h17 y80 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He has served </div><div class="t m9e x34 h17 y81 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as executive editor of </div><div class="t m9f x13 h17 y81 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministry </div><div class="t ma0 x37 h17 y81 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and on the editorial staff of </div><div class="t ma1 x38 h17 y81 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These </div><div class="t ma2 x34 h17 y82 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Times. </div><div class="t ma3 x1b h17 y82 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He began his denominational career as a pastor in Indiana and </div><div class="t ma4 x34 h17 y83 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Arizona. </div><div class="t ma5 x35 h17 y84 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Elder Holt enjoys getting involved in do-it-yourself projects, read-</div><div class="t ma6 x34 h17 y85 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing, and studying the American Civil War era. He has written numer-</div><div class="t ma7 x34 h17 y86 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ous&apos; articles for religious and secular periodicals. He and his wife, </div><div class="t ma8 x34 h17 y87 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Judy, have a son and a daughter. </div><div class="t ma9 x34 hb y88 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Blessing of Daily Study </div><div class="t maa x39 h17 y89 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Every day some portion of time should be appropriated to the </div><div class="t mab x3a h17 y8a ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of the lessons, not merely in learning to mechanically repeat the </div><div class="t mac x3a h17 y8b ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">words, while the mind does not comprehend the meaning; but to go to </div><div class="t mad x3a h17 y8c ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the very foundation, and become familiar with what is brought out in </div><div class="t mae x3a h17 y8d ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the lesson. </div><div class="t maf x3b h17 y8e ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;—Counsels on Sabbath School Work, </div><div class="t mb0 x3c h17 y8f ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 53. </div><div class="t mb1 x3a hb y90 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daily Lesson Study Pledge </div><div class="t mb2 x10 h18 y91 ff6 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">❑ </div><div class="t mb3 x39 h17 y92 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As one greatly desirous of improving my knowledge of the Scrip-</div><div class="t mb4 x10 h17 y93 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tures and of the Lord to whom they point, I pledge to carefully and </div><div class="t mb5 x10 h17 y94 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prayerfully study some portion of the Sabbath School lesson each day </div><div class="t mb6 x10 h17 y95 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the week. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
